com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.typeconversion
Class PropertyBag

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.typeconversion.PropertyBag

public final class PropertyBag
extends Object

A container for out-of-band data that an external data item editor can use to modify an Item that has been retrieved from an external data source.

Since:
4.0
